    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, combine the <strong>tamarind paste </strong>with the <strong>agave</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, 3/4 of the <strong>tamari soy sauce </strong>(save the rest for later!) and the <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>sticky</strong> <strong>tamarind marinade</strong></p>",
